title: Penny Australia x Christian Hosoi Signature Model
description:
Penny Skateboards is proud to introduce the first of their signature models with Christian Hosoi. 
Known for his raw and dynamic approach to skateboarding, Christian Hosoi brings his legendary graphic to Penny Skateboards. Featuring an epic graphic wrap and custom transparent griptape, the Hosoi Signature model is a must have for your Penny collection.

Filmed and Edited by Ryan Spencer
